<script type="application/json" id="jsonAnalytics">{"segment":"<p class=\"wb-img-align-center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/content/image/webpage/dtc_cover(1).png\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mirroring broader challenges across the wine industry, the&nbsp;annual&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sovos.com/shipcompliant/content-library/wine-dtc-report/\">Direct-to-Consumer Wine Shipping Report</a>&nbsp;from Sovos ShipCompliant&nbsp;and WineBusiness Analytics found that the prolonged downturn in the&nbsp;DtC&nbsp;wine shipping market intensified in 2025. The entire report can be downloaded for free and provides an in-depth examination of one of the most challenging years in nearly two decades as the market saw unprecedented declines of 15% by volume and&nbsp;6% by value. The report can be downloaded <a href=\"https://sovos.com/shipcompliant/content-library/wine-dtc-report/\">here</a> and includes data on shipments by winery region, varietal, price tier and winery size.</p>"}</script>
<script type="application/json" id="jsonEvents">[{"event_id":15525,"event_title":"Texas Wine & Grape Growers Association Annual Conference & Tradeshow","event_desc":"The Texas Wine & Grape Growers Association is proud to be the oldest and only statewide industry organization that supports, promotes, and legislatively addresses issues amongst vineyard owners, grape crop producers\/managers, and winery and tasting room managers\/buyers, as well as vineyard and grape crop manufacturers and distributors and winery and tasting room product and service vendors.\r\n\r\nThe Annual Conference & Trade Show features engaging educational sessions, unique food and wine events, the chance to reconnect with your wine and grape family and grow your business, and more.","event_start_date_day":23,"event_start_date_month":2,"event_start_date_year":2026,"state":"TX","country":"USA","event_start_date":"2026-02-23"},{"event_id":15523,"event_title":"Pennsylvania Winery Association Annual Membership Meeting","event_desc":"PWA Members are invited to attend the PWA Annual Membership Business Meeting on Tuesday, February 24, 2026 at the Nittany Lion Inn in State College, PA.","event_start_date_day":24,"event_start_date_month":2,"event_start_date_year":2026,"state":"PA","country":"USA","event_start_date":"2026-02-24"},{"event_id":15524,"event_title":"Virginia Winter Technical Meeting and Trade Show","event_desc":"Save the date for the 2026 Winter Technical Meeting and Tradeshow. We will be gathering at the Shenandoah Valley Conference Center at Hotel Madison in Harrisonburg, VA, on February 25-26. Meeting and registration details can be found on the website mid-December.","event_start_date_day":25,"event_start_date_month":2,"event_start_date_year":2026,"state":"VA","country":"USA","event_start_date":"2026-02-25"}]</script>


